<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>akanksha writes | publications</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #ffffff;
            --text: #1a1a1a;
            --secondary: #666666;
            --accent: #0070f3;
            --border: #eaeaea;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 750px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 80px;
        }

        .logo { font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; color: var(--text); }

        .nav-links a {
            margin-left: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--secondary);
            font-size: 0.9em;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
        .nav-links a.active { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        section { margin-bottom: 60px; }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-transform: lowercase;
            color: var(--text);
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 100px;
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            font-size: 0.85em;
            color: var(--secondary);
            text-align: center;
        }

        a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
        a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            nav { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px; }
            .nav-links a { margin-left: 0; margin-right: 15px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <a href="index.html" class="logo">akanksha.</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="index.html">home</a>
            <a href="publications.html" class="active">publications</a>
            <a href="thoughts.html">thoughts</a>
            <a href="creative.html">creative space</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header>
        <h1>Publications</h1>
    </header>

   <section>
        <h2>selected work</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--secondary);">Coming soon... a collection of my formal writings and published pieces.</p>
    </section>

    <footer>
        © 2026 Akanksha • built with simplicity
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
